data.description: Come see this gem located in Upchurch Farm Subdivision. Sitting on an almost an acre and a half! Lots of love has been added from LVP flooring in the living and dining room, a privacy fence, expanded driveway, concrete pad in the back with extended roof line, metal roof, new water heater, new A/C unit, new microwave and dishwasher. Septic tank was recently pumped in 2021.Seller is asking for a 60 day close and selling as is. Agent related to seller.
